snippet: More than 140,000 people, many decked out in bikinis, daisy crowns and signature fuzzy boots, are expected to flood into the Las Vegas Motor Speedway each night for the weekend-long Electric Daisy Carnival....

headline.print_headline: 140K Expected Each Day of Electric Daisy Carnival
headline.main: 140K Expected Each Day of Electric Daisy Carnival

lead_paragraph: More than 140,000 people, many decked out in bikinis, daisy crowns and signature fuzzy boots, are expected to flood into the Las Vegas Motor Speedway each night for the weekend-long Electric Daisy Carnival.
